data.description: Situated within the wonderful gated community of Sunrise at Parkwood Ranch offering greenbelts, community pool & spa. This light & bright beauty with an open & spacious floorplan is sure to please. New carpet recently installed and HVAC replaced in 2022. Water softener, RO and security system stay. Large  private owner suite offers a walk-in and secondary closet, oversized bath & dual vanities, The eat-in kitchen has tons of natural light, kitchen island & plenty of cabinet/counter space. SS refrigerator stays. Roomy secondary bedrooms, one with a walk-in closet, provide the perfect space for a home office, hobby room, guests or family. The interior laundry comes complete with washer/dryer. Private backyard with paver patio area and storage shed is a clean canvas for your landscape ideas.
